ons":[{"key":"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774697149756,"sessionId":"7e94af54-60fe-46a5-8d28-85f9fe52af7b","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44828,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/7e94af54-60fe-46a5-8d28-85f9fe52af7b.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job asking me to check for active sessions and potentially perform autonomous learning. Let me first check the sessions_list to see if there are any active conversations."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j4cuiqmt1fau_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774697150322}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774697155567}}
{"type":"message","id":"62bf5460","parentId":"ab977677","timestamp":"2026-03-28T11:26:00.214Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron job itself. There's no actual user conversation in the last 5 minutes. The cron job's own session doesn't count as an active user conversation. I should proceed with the autonomous learning task - searching for industry news about enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services relevant to 道简网络 (Daojian Network).","thinkingSignature":"1ac4f6bb37bddb04f8a8341adec8050d9083e34535998f8fa4ef26c18e7680a2"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有当前 cron 任务自身在运行，没有真实用户活跃对话。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_murmshqzd5hx_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":864,"output":139,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44984,"cost":{"input":0.0002592,"output":0.0001668,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017454299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774697155578}}
{"type":"message","id":"a71259ea","parentId":"62bf5460","timestamp":"2026-03-28T11:26:00.221Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_murmshqzd5hx_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774697160218}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a270a76","parentId":"a71259ea","timestamp":"2026-03-28T11:26:05.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll perform 3-5 web searches on topics relevant to 道简网络's business:\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态\n2. 智能安防行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成行业趋势\n4. IT运维服务行业动态\n5. B端科技服务行业趋势\n\nLet me run multiple searches in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"02ab4838452692a7228730c50ffededefcf8494ddb55d188ab65fd7e4609f4e3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2eb4urmtmm0p_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型最新政策 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2eb4urmtmm0p_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2eb4urmtmm0p_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业趋势 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1518,"output":239,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45738,"cost":{"input":0.00045539999999999996,"output":0.0002868,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00206163}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774697160220}}
